@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rrlatm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.exp(0.20) * wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.41)))
    v0 = 0.84
    v1 = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.95 + v0 + 0.38) * wp.cos(v2 + 0.18)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.45) * ((v2 + 0.08 - v2 + 0.96) * v2))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.25)))
    data[tid] = v0
